1. Install.

./configure
make
sudo make install


2. Run.

xcurf /path/to/pixmap/for/layout1.png /path/to/pixmap/for/layout2.png [/path/to/pixmap/for/layout3.png /path/to/pixmap/for/layout4.png]


3. Example, in ENG-RU system:

xcurf /usr/local/share/gxneur/pixmaps/en.png /usr/local/share/gxneur/pixmaps/ru.png


4. More pixmaps for layout see here
http://xneur.ru/browser/icons
